<br>
Also, comparing a 51 warrior and a 51 wizard for damage output on tough mobs, the wizard is definately needed to supplement damage.<br>
<br>
The imbalance comes from the exceptional performance of melee against low blue, and from the exceptional performance of all melee at the very highest levels, in my opinion.  And the melee defense is a bigger imbalance than the melee offense, because it is the defense that makes &quot;constant pull&quot; an option.<br>
<br>
I don't think they really have the option to completely rethink their melee formulas, though.  I have some hope for the luclin expansion's caster items.  But, you do have to recognize that they have overpowered melee, and we're just dealing with mudflation if luclin brings magical damage back up.<br>
